WEBVTT

00:00:00.532 --> 00:00:04.644
Hajdemo pričati prljavo.

00:00:04.644 --> 00:00:07.380
Prije nekoliko godina, začudo,

00:00:07.380 --> 00:00:10.114
trebala sam ići na zahod

00:00:10.114 --> 00:00:13.464
i uspjela sam ga pronaći, javni WC,

00:00:13.464 --> 00:00:15.828
i ušla sam u kabinu,

00:00:15.828 --> 00:00:19.125
i htjela napraviti ono što radim
čitav svoj život:

00:00:19.125 --> 00:00:23.667
poslužiti se toaletom, pustiti vodu
i zaboraviti na to.

00:00:23.667 --> 00:00:25.748
Iz nekog sam se razloga toga dana

00:00:25.748 --> 00:00:27.932
zapitala nešto:

00:00:27.932 --> 00:00:31.808
gdje to sve odlazi?